{"image_id": "KSU_2014_page_72", "image_size": [1238, 1613], "ocr": [{"text": "Kansas City Southern and Subsidiaries", "bbox": [444.7, 109.4, 793.3, 132.5]}, {"text": "Notes to Consolidated Financial Statements-(Continued)", "bbox": [368.3, 144.8, 869.6, 167.9]}, {"text": "66", "bbox": [608.6, 1506.2, 629.4, 1529.2]}, {"text": "In the first half of 2013, the Company entered into foreign currency forward contracts with an aggregate notional amount", "bbox": [130.3, 193.8, 1145.7, 216.9]}, {"text": "of $325.0 million. These contracts matured on December 31, 2013, and obligated the Company to purchase a total of Ps.4,202.3", "bbox": [84.4, 218.8, 1156.6, 241.9]}, {"text": "million at a weighted-average exchange rate of Ps.12.93 to each U.S. dollar. During December 2013, the Company entered into", "bbox": [84.4, 243.8, 1151.4, 266.9]}, {"text": "offsetting contracts with an aggregate notional amount of $324.3 million. These offsetting contracts matured on December 31,", "bbox": [84.4, 268.8, 1141.6, 291.9]}, {"text": "2013, and obligated the Company sell a total of Ps.4,202.3 million at a weighted-average exchange rate of Ps.12.96 to each U.S.", "bbox": [84.4, 293.8, 1158.1, 316.9]}, {"text": "dollar.", "bbox": [84.4, 318.8, 142.3, 341.9]}, {"text": "In 2014 and 2013, the Company did not designate any of the foreign currency forward contracts as hedging instruments", "bbox": [130.3, 362.6, 1133.0, 385.7]}, {"text": "for accounting purposes, and the related net loss was recognized in foreign exchange gain (loss) within the consolidated", "bbox": [84.4, 387.6, 1088.9, 410.7]}, {"text": "statements of comprehensive income.", "bbox": [84.4, 412.6, 398.2, 435.7]}, {"text": "As of December 31, 2013, the Company had no outstanding foreign currency forward contracts.", "bbox": [130.3, 456.4, 931.3, 479.4]}, {"text": "The following table presents the fair value of derivative instruments included in the consolidated balance sheets (in", "bbox": [130.3, 500.1, 1095.1, 523.2]}, {"t